01:06:40.953 --> 01:06:42.303
Incoming livestream: So…

35
01:06:44.203 --> 01:06:56.042
Incoming livestream: First, we'll look at, some, policy generation. So we have a skill that's shipped with this that just has the procedural knowledge about Cedar, and some instructions on how to call these different tools that are exposed.

36
01:06:56.113 --> 01:07:08.392
Incoming livestream: So, first we have the agent actually fetch the available context and values, right, that are available for these entities, and maybe we're just gonna start writing a policy, and we'll tell it to go write some policies for shell injection.

